title: a Homage to TFG1-Vol.1-UT3-Mod
description:
a homage to TFG1 


is the first volume released to the public,
which contains 57 Characters, 41 AlternateModes 
and some 35-plus chapters.

Later volumes will be comprised of more characters and chapters,
alternate UI, etc.

Featuring some unique content, made specifically for the UT3 engine,
consisting of new character meshes, environmental meshes, textures, materials
The characters are made from scratch, modeled to TFG1.
